C.7 verify (2026-05-13):

C.7 = smoke E2E: approval round-trip with both decisions.
kind: verify-only (no source files changed).

To avoid extra SMS to operator phone during the back-to-back runs,
agent_settings.approval_channel was temporarily removed before C.7 and
restored to 'sms' after. Both runs decided via curl POST /v1/approvals/:id
(JWT auth) — the SMS-reply path is independently covered by C.6 live e2e.

