Verification matrix for session 1:
  ✓ approval_requested → approval_granted → output_dispatched landed in order
  ✓ output_dispatched names all 3 recipients (SES SendEmailCommand → one
     message with To: dmrknife@gmail.com,dmrknife+c7a@gmail.com,dmrknife+c7b@gmail.com)
  ✓ SES returned a messageId; result.json from send_email tool exposes it.
  ✓ Run reached `completed` status

(Plan spec said "output_dispatched × 3" but SES is a multi-recipient
fan-out where ONE SendEmailCommand carries multiple ToAddresses, so one
output_dispatched row covers all 3 — confirmed in worker/src/tools/send_email.ts
where the activity emit happens after the single SES call returns.)

